This PR contains a fix to a bug which cleared the reponse content if the status code is changed via a [`Resource` parameter described in the documentation](https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/advanced/response-change-status-code/#use-a-response-parameter). 

Sample code which creates an empty response body:

```python
@app.delete(
    "/{id}",
    responses={
        204: {"model": None, "description": "No Content"},
    },
    status_code=204,
)
async def delete_deployment(
    id: str = Path(None),
    response: Response = None,
) -> None:
    response.status_code = 400
    return {"msg": "Status overwritten"}
```

